snippet.title: Amber Heard. The Villain Or The Victim?
snippet.description:
Hollywood actress and model Amber Heard, has been in much controversy after her separation and divorce with Hollywood actor Johnny Depp. Is she the real manipulator of this story? Recent news have pointed out that Amber Heard was the real perpetrator of the abuse that went on in her and Johnny Depp's relationship.






Amber Heard is and American actress, mostly known for her roles in "Aquaman", "The Rum Diary" where she collaborated with Johnny Depp. "Justice League", "Zombieland" and "Never Back Down". In this video, we capture recordings and short clips of Amber Heard, hurling abuse at Johnny Depp, as well as showing the manipulative and cynical side of her. Come and take a look for more info. Is she the villain or just a victim? Please write down your opinions down below in the comments!
